%% Supplier Portal — Phase 2: Transactional Enablement
%% Split from 01_e2e_process_flow.mmd

flowchart TB
    AA([Supplier Dashboard<br/>Financial Summary + Tasks + Alerts]) --> BB{Supplier<br/>Action?}

    BB -->|View POs| CC[Purchase Order List<br/>8 POs, Multi-Buyer]
    BB -->|Create Invoice| DD[Invoice List<br/>16 Invoices, Lifecycle Nav]
    BB -->|Update Profile| EE[Supplier Profile<br/>5-Tab Read/Edit View]

    CC --> FF[PO Detail View<br/>Billing, Summary, Line Items]
    FF --> GG{PO Status?}

    GG -->|Ack Pending| HH[Click Acknowledge<br/>or Bulk Acknowledge via Actions]
    GG -->|Acknowledged| II[Click Create Invoice<br/>— PO Flip Entry Point]
    GG -->|Rejected| JJ[Read-Only —<br/>No Actions Available]
    GG -->|Closed| JJ

    HH --> KK[AGENT: Purchase Order<br/>Automated — Sync Ack to ERP]
    KK --> II

    II --> LL[Select Lines to<br/>Create Invoice Modal]
    LL --> MM[Partial Line Selection<br/>1 of N Lines]
    MM --> NN[Invoice Draft Created<br/>Auto-Populated from PO Data]

    NN --> OO{Add More<br/>PO Lines?}
    OO -->|Yes| PP[Select PO Lines to<br/>Add to Invoice Modal]
    PP --> NN
    OO -->|No| QQ[Edit Mode: Fill Invoice No,<br/>Adjust Dates, Payment Terms]

    DD --> RR{Creation<br/>Method?}
    RR -->|PO Flip| II
    RR -->|Manual| SS[Click + Add Invoice<br/>Blank Draft Created]

    SS --> TT[Edit Mode: Fill ALL Fields<br/>Bill-to, Ship-to, Type, PO No.]

    QQ --> UU[Save Draft]
    TT --> UU

    UU --> VV[Attach Files via Files Tab<br/>Upload, Auto-Classify, Preview]
    VV --> WW[Submit Invoice]
    WW --> XX[AGENT: Portal Invoice Creation<br/>Assisted — Validate & Sync to AP]

    XX --> YY{Invoice<br/>Lifecycle}
    YY -->|Draft| WW
    YY -->|Submitted| ZZ[AP Team Processes<br/>— Read-Only for Supplier]
    YY -->|In Progress| ZZ
    YY -->|Rejected| AAA[Supplier Creates<br/>New Corrected Invoice]
    YY -->|Paid| BBB([Terminal: Payment<br/>Complete])
    YY -->|Void| CCC([Terminal: Invoice<br/>Voided])

    EE --> DDD{Profile<br/>Change?}
    DDD -->|Edit Data| EEE[AGENT: Master Data Change<br/>Approval — Assisted Workflow]
    EEE --> FFF{Change<br/>Approved?}
    FFF -->|Yes| GGG[Update Supplier<br/>Master Record]
    FFF -->|No| HHH[Reject Change —<br/>Notify Supplier]
    DDD -->|View Only| AA

    style KK fill:#ff6b6b,color:#fff
    style XX fill:#ffa726,color:#fff
    style EEE fill:#ffa726,color:#fff
